<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Trang web đang bảo trì</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Be+Vietnam+Pro:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f4f4f5;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --text: #1a1a1a;
        --muted: #64748b;
        --brand: #8b5a2b;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
        font-family: "Be Vietnam Pro", system-ui, sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #fff 0%, var(--bg) 55%);
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 440px;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 28px 36px;
        background: var(--surface);
        border-radius: 22px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.9);
      }
      .icon {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        margin: 0 auto 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.1);
        color: var(--brand);
      }
      .icon svg { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .domain {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        color: #334155;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="card">
      <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
          <path d="M12 9v4" />
          <path d="M12 17h.01" />
          <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h1>Trang web đang bảo trì</h1>
      <p>Landing page này đã được tắt tạm thời trong hệ thống quản trị. Vui lòng quay lại sau.</p>
      <% if (domain) { %>
      <span class="domain"><%= domain %></span>
      <% } %>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
